<para>A text label. </para>
    </simplesect>
        <simplesect>
            <title>Detailed Description</title>

<para> Its position is defined by the member <emphasis>position</emphasis> and the setting of <link linkend="class_q_c_p_item_text_1a781cdf8c640fc6a055dcff1e675c8c7a">setPositionAlignment</link>. The latter controls which part of the text rect shall be aligned with <emphasis>position</emphasis>.</para>

<para>The text alignment itself (i.e. left, center, right) can be controlled with <link linkend="class_q_c_p_item_text_1ab5bc0684c4d1bed81949a11b34dba478">setTextAlignment</link>.</para>

<para>The text may be rotated around the <emphasis>position</emphasis> point with <link linkend="class_q_c_p_item_text_1a4bcc10cd97952c3f749d75824b5077f0">setRotation</link>. </para>
